label_shopee_deemed_consent_popup_conten:
For benefit of our users, Shopee may carry various activities for marketing and communications, including:

  • Sending marketing and communications for our products and services through SMS, Email by Shopee and/or our affiliates;
  • Sharing your information to our affiliates for marketing and communications purpose by the affiliates.

You may change your preference for marketing and communication by visiting the web setting page or ‘Read more’ button below to learn more. Please update Shopee application to fully utilize the setting features.
